If one wants to include the link to an attachment in a page, one would open the "link" dialog by clicking the appropriate button above the markup text area.  Then, one would select the "Attachments" tab.

That tab lists all the attachments by file name, but doesn't give the comments associated to them upon uploading. That is sometimes cumbersome, if the file names are not very meaningful, but still reasonable to use, e.g. offer numbers or part numbers.

Please include the comment of attachments in the chooser dialog.

